tool_description: Formula 1 data for the ultimate motorsport fanatic!
name: F1 Live Motorsport Data
title: F1 Live Motorsport Data

api_list.name: Session
api_list.description: Provides session details for a given `session id` found in the Races endpoint. Contains information on drivers times, session weather, speed traps, and session status. Updated throughout each session.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://f1-live-motorsport-data.p.rapidapi.com/session/2757"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "f1-live-motorsport-data.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
